X:1
T:DYNAMICS Test
M:4/4
L:1/4
K:C
%%DYNAMICS curve linear
%%DYNAMICS transition 8
%%DYNAMICS attack 1.3
%
% Start piano, crescendo to forte over 8 notes (linear curve)
!p! C D E F | G A B c |
% Now jump to fortissimo — should glide over 8 notes
!ff! c B A G | F E D C |
%
% Switch to exponential curve (slow start, fast finish)
%%DYNAMICS curve exponential
!p! C E G c | e g a b |
!f! c' b a g | e c G E |
%
% Logarithmic curve (fast start, slow finish)
%%DYNAMICS curve logarithmic
%%DYNAMICS transition 4
!pp! C D E F | !fff! G A B c |
%
% Turn off — should revert to instant jumps
%%DYNAMICS off
!p! C D E F | !ff! G A B c |]
